<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṉ viraṉ kolaṅkariyāṉāṉa veṇāvuṭaiyār Uttamacoḻaviṇṇakarāḻvār koyil Attamaṇṭapattukku kiḻakku perumāḷum maṉṉaṉārum Eḻuntaru
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ḷiyirukkiṟa Antarāḷamaṇṭamun tirumuṉpu ma<hi rend="grantha">hā</hi>maṇṭapamum copāṉamum Ivar ceyvitta <hi rend="grantha">dharmmam § svastiśrī §</hi>
